OL,6,FA driver threw a hot takeaway meal
OL,7,Finto a British Gas engineer's face
OL,8,Fduring a fit of road rage.
OL,10,FSimon Lloyd hurled his tray of curry,
OL,11,Fchips and rice through the window of
OL,12,Fhis Range Rover on Roman Road in
OL,13,FHoylake on 25 August 2022.
OL,15,Fheard how Neil Reeve had just finished
OL,16,Fa job on North Parade at around 1pm.
