OL,4,Cfit of road rage
OL,6,FLloyd tried to overtake the engineer
OL,7,Fon Roman Road in his silver Range
OL,8,FRover, but was unable to do so because
OL,9,Fof another car being in front of the
OL,10,Fwhite van.
OL,12,FThe 47-year-old, of Bertram Close in
OL,13,FMeols, then proceeded to drive
OL,14,Falongside Mr Reeve on the wrong side
OL,15,Fof the road.
OL,17,FBoth had their windows down, and Mr
OL,18,FReeve asked him: "What are you doing?"
