OL,6,FLiverpool Crown Court heard how a
OL,7,Ffurious Lloyd responded by shouting
OL,8,Fand swearing.
OL,10,FHe then threw the curry, chips and
OL,11,Frice through the window of his Range
OL,12,FRover on Roman Road in Hoylake on the
OL,13,FWirral.
OL,15,FSarah Holt, prosecuting, described how
OL,16,Fthe defendant then overtook him, but
OL,17,Fstopped at the roadside.JAs Mr Reeve
OL,18,Fpassed him, he was hit by the meal
OL,19,Fthat the other driver had purchased at
OL,20,Fa chip shop moments earlier.
