OL,6,FResidents living in a nearby house
OL,7,Ftook Mr Reeve in and gave him a cup of
OL,8,Ftea.JLloyd subsequently told
OL,9,Fdetectives under interview that the
OL,10,FBritish Gas Driver had verbally abused
OL,11,Fand spat at him, and that he threw his
OL,12,Ffood in "reflex in the heat of the
OL,13,Fmoment".
