OL,3,CDriver chucks chippy tea on man in a
OL,4,Cfit of road rage
OL,6,FHe has also been told to pay court
OL,7,Fcosts of #2,000, #500 in compensation
OL,8,Fand a victim surcharge, which must be
OL,9,Fpaid within three months.JSentencing,
OL,10,FJudge David Potter said: "For a man in
OL,11,Fhis mid-40s of previous good
OL,12,Fcharacter, it is baffling to this
OL,13,Fcourt that you should be facing
OL,14,Fsentence having been convicted by a
OL,15,Fjury.J"What happened was inappropriate
OL,16,Fand criminally wrong. It is clear to
OL,17,Fthis court that you need to undertake
OL,18,Fwork with regards to your temper when
OL,19,Ffaced with stressful situations."
